data.description: Hard to find Gem in sought after Fairway Village 55+ community that features golf, a wonderful Clubhouse with exercise equipment, events, swimming pool, library, game room & more. Master Suite with walk in closet. Kitchen has breakfast bar & large pantry located between dining and oversized family rm. Cozy gas fireplace in FR. Slider leads to private covered patio. Beautiful low maintenance yard with raised garden bed.LeafGuard gutters.
